<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head.ejs') %> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/contacto-style.css">
    <title>BiciMundo-Contacto</title>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %> 
    <main>
        <section class="contacto">
            <h2 class="contacto-header"><span>Contactanos</span>, estamos para asesorarte</h2>
            <article class="contacto-datos">
                <p>Dejanos tu consulta y a la brevedad nos pondremos en contacto con vos.</p>
                <p>Tambi√©n podes encontrarnos:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>4982-1111 / 4982-2222</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-comment-sms"></i>+5491156781234</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i>ventas@bicimundo.com</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-solid fa-location-pin"></i>Av. Central 123, CABA, BA, Argentina</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-regular fa-clock"></i>10hs a 18hs</li>
                </ul>
                <div class="contacto-social-media">
                    <a href="https://es-la.facebook.com" target="_blanck"><i class="fa-brands fa-facebook"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://twitter.com/?lang=es" target="_blanck"><i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i></a>
                    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/" target="_blanck"><i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i></a>
                </div>
            </article>
            <div class="contact-form">
                <form action="/" method="GET">
                    <div>
                        <label for="contact-name" class="form-label">Nombre y Apellido</label>
                        <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="contactName" required minLenght="2">
                        <span class="feedback"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="contact-email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                        <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="contactEmail" required pattern="[a-z0-9._%+-]+@[a-z0-9.-]+\.[a-z]{2,4}$">
                        <span class="feedback"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="contact-phone" class="form-label">Telefono</label>
                        <input type="telephone" id="contact-phone" name="contactPhone">
                        <span class="feedback"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label for="contact-data" class="form-label">Consulta</label>
                        <textarea name="contactData" id="contact-data" maxlength="400" cols="40" rows="10" placeholder="Contanos tu consulta (max. 400 caracteres)" required></textarea>
                        <span class="feedback"></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="contact-submit">
                        <button type="submit">Enviar<i class="fa-solid fa-circle-chevron-right"></i></button>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %> 
  
</body>
</html>
